fr:mainmatter.fr:p:
By the proof of initiality of the Kleisli category, the comparison functor
  sends objects c\in  C_T to the free algebras F^Tc. To prove that this
  functor is fully faithful, note that it must commute with the transposition
  actions, as in 




    \usepackage{tikz, tikz-cd, mathtools, amssymb}
