    \begin {tikzcd}
      C_T(c, c')\ar [dr, leftrightarrow]\ar [rr, "K"] & & C^T(F^Tc, F^Tc')\ar [dl, leftrightarrow] \\
      & C(c, Tc')\makebox [0pt][l]{.}
    \end {tikzcd}


 As such, this action of K is a bijection, as desired.

